dashboards.description: Dashboard to show the CIS3.0 compliance

savedSearches.displayName: Number of Old DB Passwords (5 years)

uiConfig.queryString: Time >= dateRelative(30day) and 'Log Source' = CISIdentityKeyRotation and 'Log Origin' = 'cis_identity_and_access_management_1-11.csv' | fields -Entity, -'Entity Type', -'Host Name (Server)', -'Problem Priority', -Label, 'User Name', 'Date Created', -'Log Source' | timestats span = 1day distinctcount('User Name') as OldDBPassword_Count by 'User Name'

savedSearches.displayName: CIS Default security list allowing traffic

uiConfig.queryString: Time >= dateRelative(1day) and 'Log Source' = CISNetworking and 'Log Origin' = 'cis_networking_2-5.csv' | stats count as logrecords by Region, 'Display Name' | sort -logrecords
Time >= dateRelative(30day, day) and 'Log Source' = CISLoggingMonitoringVCNLogs | timestats distinctcount(Identifier) as NumofSubnetswithoutLogs by Region

savedSearches.displayName: CIS Public bucket count with trend

uiConfig.queryString: 'Log Source' = CISObjectstorage and 'Log Origin' = 'cis_storage_object_storage_5-1-1.csv' and 'Display Name' != name | stats distinctcount('Display Name') as Total_public_buckets, trend(distinctcount('Display Name')) | compare timeshift = auto
Time >= dateRelative(90day, day) and 'Log Source' = CISSummary and Compliant = No | link span = 1day Time, Section | timestats span = 1day distinctcount(Title) as Total by Section

savedSearches.displayName: Object Storage write logs not enabled

uiConfig.queryString: Time >= dateRelative(30day) and 'Log Source' = CISLoggingMonitoringObject | stats distinctcount('Display Name') as logrecords by Region, 'Display Name' | sort -logrecords
Time >= dateRelative(90day) and 'Log Source' = CISFileStorage | link span = 1day Time, 'Display Name' | timestats distinctcount(Identifier) as TotalFS

Time >= dateRelative(30day, day) and 'Log Source' = CISBlockvolume and 'Log Origin' like 'cis_Storage_Block%5-2-2.csv' and KMS_key_id = None | fields -Entity, -'Entity Type', -'Host Name (Server)', -'Problem Priority', -Label, -'Log Origin', 'Display Name', 'Availability Domain', -KMS_key_id, Region, -'Log Source' | stats count as logrecords by Region, 'Display Name'
'Log Source' = CISCompute and 'Log Origin' = 'cis_compute_3-2.csv' | stats count as logrecords by Region, 'Compartment ID', 'Display Name'

savedSearches.displayName: Count of Users - Old Secret Key

uiConfig.queryString: Time >= dateRelative(30day) and 'Log Source' = CISIdentitySecretkey_90days | fields -Entity, -'Entity Type', -'Host Name (Server)', -'Problem Priority', -Label, -'Log Source' | timestats span = 1day distinctcount('User Name') as OldSecretkey_Count by 'User Name' | timecompare shift = 1day
'Log Source' = CISObjectstorage and 'Log Origin' = 'cis_storage_object_storage_5-1-1.csv' | stats distinctcount('Display Name') as PublicBuckets by 'Display Name'

Time >= dateRelative(30day) and 'Log Source' = CISIdentityKeyRotation | fields -Entity, -'Entity Type', -'Host Name (Server)', -'Problem Priority', -Label, -'Log Source' | timestats span = 1day distinctcount('User Name') as OldAuthtoken_Count by 'User Name' | timecompare shift = 1day
'Log Source' = CISCompute and 'Log Origin' = 'cis_compute_3-3.csv' | stats count as logrecords by Region, 'Compartment ID', 'Display Name'
'Log Source' = CISCompute and 'Log Origin' = 'cis_compute_3-1.csv' | stats count as logrecords by Region, 'Compartment ID', 'Display Name'

Time >= dateRelative(30day) and 'Log Source' = CISIdentityIAM45days | fields -Entity, -'Entity Type', -'Host Name (Server)', -'Problem Priority', -Label, -'Log Source' | timestats span = 1day distinctcount('Display Name') as Keynotused_45days by 'Display Name' | timecompare shift = 1day

Time >= dateRelative(90day) and 'Log Source' = CISBlockvolume and 'Log Origin' like 'cis_Storage_Block%5-2-2.csv' and KMS_key_id = null | timestats span = 1day distinctcount(Identifier) as TotalBootVolume

Time >= dateRelative(30day) and 'Log Source' = CISIdentityAPIKey_90days | fields -Entity, -'Entity Type', -'Host Name (Server)', -'Problem Priority', -Label, -'Log Source' | timestats span = 1day distinctcount('User Name') as OldAPIKey_Count by 'User Name' | timecompare shift = 1day | sort -OldAPIKey_Count, 'User Name'
Time >= dateRelative(180day) and 'Log Source' = CISSummary and Compliant != 'n/a' | link span = 1day Time, Compliant | timestats distinctcount(Title) as ComplianceCount by Compliant
'Log Source' = CISCompute | stats distinctcount(Identifier) as Identifier, trend(distinctcount(Identifier)) | compare timeshift = auto

savedSearches.displayName: CMK Not Rotated count per day in last week

uiConfig.queryString: Time >= dateRelative(90day) and 'Log Source' = CISLoggingMonitoringCMK | timestats span = 1day distinctcount('Display Name') as CMKCount by 'Display Name' | timecompare shift = 1day

Time > dateRelative(30day) and 'Log Source' = CISObjectstorage and 'Log Origin' like 'cis_Storage_Object%5-1-2.csv' and KMS_key_id = None | stats distinctcount('Display Name') as Total_buckets_without_CMK, trend(distinctcount('Display Name'))

Time >= dateRelative(30day, day) and 'Log Source' = CISBlockvolume and 'Log Origin' like 'cis_Storage_Block%5-2-1.csv' and KMS_key_id = None | fields -Entity, -'Entity Type', -'Host Name (Server)', -'Problem Priority', -Label, -'Log Source', -'Log Origin', 'Display Name', 'Availability Domain', -KMS_key_id, Region | stats count as logrecords by Region, 'Display Name'

Time >= dateRelative(1day) and 'Log Source' = CISSummary and Compliant != 'n/a' | eval 'CIS Title' = 'Recommendation Name' || ' - ' || Title | eval CISlevel = 'Level -' || Level | eval percent = toNumber(substr(Compliance_Percentage, 0, length(Compliance_Percentage) - 1)) | where percent != 100 | stats distinctcount('CIS Title') by CISlevel, Section, 'CIS Title', Compliance_Percentage

Time >= dateRelative(90day) and 'Log Source' = CISBlockvolume and 'Log Origin' like 'cis_Storage_Block%5-2-1.csv' and KMS_key_id = null | timestats span = 1day distinctcount(Identifier) as logrecords by 'Display Name' | timecompare shift = 1day
Time >= dateRelative(1day) and 'Log Source' = CISNetworking and 'Log Origin' = 'cis_networking_2-2.csv' | fields 'Log Origin' | stats count as logrecords by Region, 'Display Name' | sort -logrecords

Time > dateRelative(30day) and 'Log Source' = CISObjectstorage and 'Log Origin' like 'cis_Storage_Object%5-1-3.csv' and Object_Versioning = disabled and 'Display Name' != name | stats distinctcount('Display Name') as logrecords by Region, 'Display Name'

Time >= dateRelative(1day) and 'Log Source' = CISNetworking and 'Log Origin' = 'cis_networking_2-1.csv' | fields 'Log Origin' | stats distinctcount(Identifier) as logrecords by Region, 'Display Name' | sort -logrecords
